{"tid":1473171,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"［知乎］如何看待环球时报记者付国豪在香港机场的遭遇及事件后续?","createTime":"2019-08-14T18:38:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-15T07:37:32.000Z","uid":55511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"449679d5812122739dba66169fd9249203ea01d6","tid":1473171,"uid":55511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T18:38:45.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.zhihu.com/question/340424050\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.zhihu.com%2Fquestion%2F340424050&d=uCt0JTl3CznPmZ5dgdQegx6eP3a%2FjAUraAi1lUB%2B7iI%3D&h=9a9428aa\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.zhihu.com/question/340424050</a><br />\n<br />\n簡評：<br />\n入邊有好多人都係借題發揮 借機表達對香港現況既理解或者情緒宣洩<br />\n並用呢個slogan文宣調整左下知乎人既意識形態<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YUnGXm7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYUnGXm7.jpg&h=7eb14d36&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n隨著知乎素質越黎越低 大家睇到呢啲立場撚 帶風向撚好難唔睇到嬲。<br />\n內地對香港事件既報導一直都係以 抺黑示威者做暴徒同港獨 兼且以警察同愛國者所遭受既暴力為主。<br />\n做成大陸人對香港示威既反對 同表示對香港示威者既憤怒 有唔少人被煽動 卻混然不知。<br />\n我地姑且入去睇下到底係咩論調"},{"pid":"289b7e63903a5a681613a3ce89a671b514f07358","tid":1473171,"uid":55511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T18:42:41.000Z","msg":"附：不久前知乎都係禁止討論關於香港既話題 <br />\n然後最近岩岩先借呢個問題解封<br />\n我地可以睇下呢個曾經係其中一個高質既討論平台<br />\n對香港到底係咩立場"},{"pid":"448067ade5d1987e4818c26d1663be22d124da62","tid":1473171,"uid":272353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T18:45:27.000Z","msg":"其實明明係shame of HKpopo<br />\n支持佢地嘅人就會被民憤攻擊<br />\n睇得出popo做嘅野已經冇（正常）人原諒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"195dff090b64b87d2615e75e7ed7d54dce77e90a","tid":1473171,"uid":49197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T18:47:05.000Z","msg":"知乎自從被滲透同打壓後已收皮<br />\n上品葱啦"},{"pid":"0bda84771317539c3a316a88159ee834d41207cf","tid":1473171,"uid":50211,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T18:47:29.000Z","msg":"唔好意思阻一阻你<br />\n<br />\n817光復紅土無人提？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1473127\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1473127</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"d0148ea8b4c89285a3f9751f594230241758626a","tid":1473171,"uid":201356,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T19:29:53.000Z","msg":"知乎上嘅人對香港人無好感係真.無法轉變<br />\n佢哋唔係同我哋同一個想像的共同體 自然乜都拉埋上「港獨」、分離思潮 (即使只係普通嘅不同)<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢哋亦難以接受香港同中國 (確切啲嚟講，係香港人同中國人之間) 有住根本嘅唔同<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 佢哋淨係覺得(亦淨係可以接受)香港只不過係一個富裕啲嘅中國城市 其他一切亦無興趣去了解<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我喺知乎睇咗好幾年，已經見無數香港po主畀人逐一打成「港獨」(好在我冇出過回答) <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n即使啲回覆舐得大陸幾盡、踩得自己幾盡都好 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢哋最經典嗰句：你即使唔係意識到你自己係港毒你至少都係個50%港毒分子 (大意) <del>好有土改文革feel</del><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n可以話你其實講乜根本無人在乎 亦無人想將你當中國人看待你們想多了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"178a87b558ab59a2fc936b0214def0ebae32f591","tid":1473171,"uid":201356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T19:34:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><a href=\"http://www.zhihu.com/question/340424050\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.zhihu.com%2Fquestion%2F340424050&d=uCt0JTl3CznPmZ5dgdQegx6eP3a%2FjAUraAi1lUB%2B7iI%3D&h=9a9428aa\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.zhihu.com/question/340424050</a><br />\n<br />\n簡評：<br />\n入邊有好多人都係借題發揮 借機表達對香港現況既理解或者情緒宣洩<br />\n並用呢個slogan文宣調整左下知乎人既意識形態<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YUnGXm7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYUnGXm7.jpg&h=7eb14d36&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n隨著知乎素質越黎越低 大家睇到呢啲立場撚 帶風向撚好難唔睇到嬲。<br />\n內地對香港事件既報導一直都係以 抺黑示威者做暴徒同港獨 兼且以警察同愛國者所遭受既暴力為主。<br />\n做成大陸人對香港示威既反對 同表示對香港示威者既憤怒 有唔少人被煽動 卻混然不知。<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">我地姑且入去睇下</span>到底係咩論調</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔使「我哋姑且」<br />\n一早已經唔應該睇<br />\n浪費精力睇一啲增值唔到自己上高係一件好無聊嘅事<br />\n打開門你會發覺出面空氣好清新 (如果咁啱無支那人就perfect了)"},{"pid":"d7e4a8908e682500dc2edf159ae2184ffe7b6e81","tid":1473171,"uid":274612,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T21:38:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/S7VEK2u.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FS7VEK2u.png&h=ff377841&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"14ed69eed41818c43d3b2da33bc63ca9ef70d26a","tid":1473171,"uid":55511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T07:37:32.000Z","msg":"咁都比人啲del<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Ast7cOL.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAst7cOL.png&h=907ffa18&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}